Serialized Form

  • Package de.copepod.tonion

    • Class de.copepod.tonion.TotemLayout extends Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      -7411804673224730902L

      • Serialized Fields

        • vgap

          int vgap
          This is the vertical gap (in pixels) which specifies the space between items. They can be changed at any time. This should be a non negative integer.
           
          See Also:
          TotemLayout.getVgap(), TotemLayout.setVgap(int)

        • dimMin

          Dimension dimMin
          TotemLayout remembers the minimum size of its components. Adding or deleting a component causes the minimum size to be recalculated. The update is passed up the TOnion layers to the outside, therefore TotemLayout must know the component it is assigned to. TotemLayout can not be shared between components.

        • dimMax

          Dimension dimMax
          TotemLayout remembers the maximum size of its components. Adding or deleting a component causes the maximum size to be recalculated. The update is passed up the TOnion layers to the outside, therefore TrainLayout must know the component it is assigned to. TotemLayout can not be shared between components.

        • self

          Container self
          This is the container TotemLayout is assigned to.
